Create-react-app will creates the following folders in the main folder called "hello-react"

1 - node_modules
  where there are installed all the packages we need to launch our application, 
  they are also write in the file package-lock.json
  and their version are in the file package.json 

2 - public 
  here there is the file that the browser will read to load the page,
  only the files in public folder can be used in the file public/index.html
  
3 - src 
  we will insert here folders and files in Javascript 
  because the file src/index.js is connected to the public/index.html
